==Trivia==
*The Mysterious Old Man appeared before the [[Bandits of the Golden Claw]] on two occasions. During the first he appeared before the group, who were not sure how he got into the cave system, only leaving after [[Davey]] spoke to him.{{CiteNPC|npc=Arthur Artimus|quote=A mysterious old man turned up today. Not sure how he got in. Kept pestering us until eventually Davey spoke to him, at which point he offloaded a load of spinach rolls onto us then left.|loc=Feathered journal}} On the second occasion, the group ignored the Mysterious Old Man, resulting in them being teleported away.{{CiteNPC|npc=Arthur Artimus|quote=That mysterious old man has turned up again. We don't have time for this, quite frankly, so we're just going to ignore him, after all what could be possibl... |loc=Feathered journal}}
*If the Mysterious Old Man spawns underwater, he will be wearing diving gear.
*If the Mysterious Old Man spawns underwater, members can also receive a singular item akin to how he works for free-to-play players.
*The Mysterious Old Man can be found upstairs in a house in eastern [[Falador]], saying he is trying to solve a puzzle-cube and that he is retired.

